Class MessageForwarder

java.lang.Object
it.polimi.ingsw.observer.MessageForwarder
Direct Known Subclasses:
Client, GameInitializationManager, GameManager, RemoteView, SocketConnection, Turn, View
public abstract class MessageForwarder
extends java.lang.Object
Encompasses all the Receiver and Sender for all the message type, necessary for the correct functioning of the game messages.
